'''Amine Gülşe''' is a Swedish-Turkish actress, model and beauty pageant titleholder born and raised in Sweden. She was crowned [[Miss Turkey|Miss Turkey 2014]] and represented her country at the [[Miss World 2014]] pageant.

==Life and career==
Gülşe's mother is from Izmir, Turkey and her father is an [[Iraqi Turkmen]] from [[Kirkuk]], Iraq. She has a brother named Şahan Gülşe. Born and raised in [[Gothenburg]], Sweden.

She currently resides in [[Istanbul]], Turkey where she works as an actress and a model.<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.missworld.com/Contestants/Turkey/ |title=Archived copy |access-date=2015-08-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120720005309/http://www.missworld.com/Contestants/Turkey/ |archive-date=2012-07-20 |dead-url=yes |df= }}</ref><ref>[https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=883256808357251&set=a.138164369533169.27256.138158146200458&type=1&theater Miss Turkey 2014 - Profile]</ref> 
She starred in the 2015 Turkish television series ''Asla Vazgeçmem''.<ref name="rad150215">{{cite news |first=Hakan |last=Gence |newspaper=[[Radikal]] |publisher=[[Doğan Media Group]] |location=[[Istanbul]] |title=Amine Gülşe: Seksi olmak için illa ten göstermek gerekmez |language=Turkish |url=http://www.radikal.com.tr/fotogaleri/hayat/amine_gulse_seksi_olmak_icin_illa_ten_gostermek_gerekmez-1293710 |date=15 February 2015 |accessdate=3 March 2015}}</ref><ref name="mlyt150203">{{cite news |first= |last= |newspaper=[[Milliyet]] |publisher=[[Demirören Group]] |location=[[Istanbul]] |title=Asla Vazgeçmem dizisinin yayın tarihi belli oldu |language=Turkish |url=http://www.milliyet.com.tr/asla-vazgecmem-dizisinin-yayin-magazin-2007989/ |date=3 February 2015 |accessdate=3 March 2015}}</ref><ref name="mswotr150225">{{cite news|publisher=[[Miss World]] |title=Miss Turkey In Hit New TV Show |url=http://www.missworld.com/News/2015-02-25/Miss-Turkey-In-Hit-New-TV-Show/ |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150413061201/http://www.missworld.com/News/2015-02-25/Miss-Turkey-In-Hit-New-TV-Show/ |dead-url=yes |archive-date=13 April 2015 |date=25 February 2015 |accessdate=3 March 2015 }}</ref> Since 2017 Gülşe has been dating footballer [[Mesut Özil]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.101greatgoals.com/news/social/mesut-ozil-gets-super-close-to-former-miss-turkey-amine-gulse/|title=Mesut Ozil gets super close to former Miss Turkey, Amine Gulse|date=28 June 2017|publisher=|accessdate=23 August 2017}}</ref>

==Pageantry==

===Miss Turkey 2014===
Gülşe won Miss Turkey 2014 and was crowned as Miss World Turkey.<ref name="mlyt140530">{{cite news |first=Senem |last=Aydin |newspaper=[[Milliyet]] |publisher=[[Demirören Group]] |location=[[Istanbul]] |title=AZRA YAPTIYSA BEN DE YAPARIM |language=Turkish |url=http://cadde.milliyet.com.tr/2014/05/30/HaberDetay/1889793/azra-yaptiysa-ben-de-yaparim |date=30 May 2014 |accessdate=3 March 2015}}</ref>  The Miss Turkey pageant for 2014 was held at the Star TV Studios in Istanbul on May 27.<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.globalbeauties.com/blog/2014/05/miss-turkey-2014/ |title=Miss Turkey 2014 - Results |access-date=2015-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140602095455/http://www.globalbeauties.com/blog/2014/05/miss-turkey-2014/ |archive-date=2014-06-02 |dead-url=yes |df= }}</ref> After a year she crowned Ecem Cirpan as her successor.

===Miss World 2014===
Gülşe competed at [[Miss World 2014]] but did not place in the finals.<ref name="mlyt140908">{{cite news |newspaper=[[Milliyet]] |publisher=[[Demirören Group]] |location=[[Istanbul]] |title=ÇiÇEK VE HEDiYE PEŞiNDE DEĞiLiM |language=Turkish |url=http://cadde.milliyet.com.tr/2014/09/08/HaberDetay/1936751/cicek-ve-hediye-pesinde-degilim |date=8 September 2014 |accessdate=3 March 2015}}</ref>

