'''Antonio Tartaglione''' (born 21 August 1998) is an Italian football player. He plays for [[U.S. Pistoiese 1921|Pistoiese]] as a midfielder.{{Infobox football biography | name = Antonio Tartaglione | image = | fullname = Antonio Tartaglione | birth_date = {{birth date and age|df=yes|1998|8|21}} | birth_place = [[San Vincenzo, Tuscany]], [[Italy]] | height = 173 cm | position = [[Midfielder (association football)|Midfielder]] | currentclub = [[U.S. Pistoiese 1921|Pistoiese]] | clubnumber = 6 | youthyears1 = {{0|0000}}–2017 | youthclubs1 = [[U.S. Pistoiese 1921|Pistoiese]] | years1 = 2017– | clubs1 = [[U.S. Pistoiese 1921|Pistoiese]] | caps1 = 10 | goals1 = 1 | pcupdate = 29 May 2018 }}
== Club career ==
=== Pistoiese === On 3 September 2017, Tartaglione made his professional debut for Pistoiese as a starter in a 1–0 home win over [[S.S. Monza 1912|Monza]], he was replaced by [[Gregorio Luperini]] in the 56th minute.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://uk.soccerway.com/matches/2017/09/03/italy/serie-c1/ac-pistoiese/ac-monza-brianza-1912/2568923/|title=Pistoiese vs. Monza - 3 September 2017 - Soccerway|website=uk.soccerway.com|language=en|access-date=2018-05-29}}</ref> On 15 October he scored his first professional goal in the 25th minute of a 2–2 home draw against [[A.S. Lucchese Libertas 1905|Lucchese]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://uk.soccerway.com/matches/2017/10/15/italy/serie-c1/ac-pistoiese/as-lucchese-libertas/2579797/|title=Pistoiese vs. Lucchese - 15 October 2017 - Soccerway|website=uk.soccerway.com|language=en|access-date=2018-05-29}}</ref> On 23 October he played his first entire match, a 2–2 away draw against [[U.S. Città di Pontedera|Pontedera]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://uk.soccerway.com/matches/2017/10/23/italy/serie-c1/us-pontedera-1912/ac-pistoiese/2579806/|title=Pontedera vs. Pistoiese - 23 October 2017 - Soccerway|website=uk.soccerway.com|language=en|access-date=2018-05-29}}</ref>
