ure Association]] |- |- |2018 |'''Jury Member, Film Artists' Association of Nepal (FAAN) AWARD 2074'''<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.newsofnepal.com/2018/03/31/91225/|title=FAAN AWARD|last=|first=|date=|website=|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=}}</ref> |[[Film Artists' Association of Nepal]] |- |2018 |'''Jury Member, CG Kamana Film Award 2075'''<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.kantipurdaily.com/entertainment/2018/09/12/15367203864547763.html|title=कामना फिल्म अवार्डको मनोनयन|last=|first=|date=|website=|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=}}</ref> |[[Kamana Publications]] |}
